Package packageexplorer

Class Parser

java.lang.Object
packageexplorer.Parser
All Implemented Interfaces:
ParserInterface
public class Parser
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParserInterface
This class reads a file and parses key information out of it. Forms a list of Package's which is used to generate the html-pages in HtmlBuilder class
Author:
